File: maxima-core-docs.info,  Node: Variable atrig1

 -- Variable: atrig1
     The ‘atrig1’ package contains several additional simplification
     rules for inverse trigonometric functions.  Together with rules
     already known to Maxima, the following angles are fully
     implemented: 0, \pi/6, \pi/4, \pi/3, and \pi/2. Corresponding
     angles in the other three quadrants are also available.  Do
     ‘load("atrig1");’ to use them.


